{"tid":2259503,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【國產凌凌漆走私大王】梁克遜黯然離世3年，孝順仔長情保留父親電話號碼","createTime":"2020-10-27T01:19:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T06:46:31.000Z","uid":35221,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"22d40f8ea5ea4adc18031996ca71db90b7a4f105","tid":2259503,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T01:19:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qdg6ofh1Q8BXVLT1iyZwJc9DrJU=/802x431/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6JVNFRAPRVEPHNCDQE7ZKHZU3I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fqdg6ofh1Q8BXVLT1iyZwJc9DrJU%3D%2F802x431%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6JVNFRAPRVEPHNCDQE7ZKHZU3I.jpg&h=7dadc3b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁克遜於《國產凌凌漆》飾演反派司令口中「走私大王」賴有為。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4UDpnPd0DjGG3G7p-0Z2OCgFBcc=/802x1069/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7TWBEWA36FCZDCZ3LDGLH2IHRI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4UDpnPd0DjGG3G7p-0Z2OCgFBcc%3D%2F802x1069%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7TWBEWA36FCZDCZ3LDGLH2IHRI.jpg&h=53e93725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁克遜兒子Vincent今日向《蘋果》表示，父親已於3年前離世，享年78歲。（受訪者圖片提供）<br />\n<br />\n許多綠葉演員一生不求名利默默耕耘，觀眾只認得樣子而不知道名字，到演員離世，也無人知曉，就如周星馳主演電影《國產凌凌漆》中飾演「走私大王」賴有為的綠葉王梁克遜，原來他3年前因前列腺癌病逝，享年78歲。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者昨日欲聯絡梁克遜，無意間獲悉梁克遜死訊，他細仔Vincent告訴記者，父親已於2017年8月因前列腺癌離世。Vincent表示：「多謝你對家父的邀請，可惜他在2017年8月已離開了，但我相信他會很開心有人還記得他。我只是一直保留他的號碼，作為與他朋友的聯繫。」<br />\n<br />\n梁克遜70年代開始拍過無數電視廣告、電視劇和電影，包括「你精我都精」的竹葉青和人人搬屋經典廣告，在鄭少秋版《倚天屠龍記》做陽頂天，演出過《誓不低頭》、《網中人》等劇，又拍過《點指兵兵》、《我愛夜來香》、《精裝追女仔》、《精裝追女仔II》、《陰陽錯》、《最佳拍檔女皇密令》等逾70部電影，經常演有錢人、警官、法官，當中最經典的，是《國產凌凌漆》被大反派司令指偷了恐龍骨的「走私大王」賴有為，以及《精裝追女仔II》中演司徒銘議員，上曾志偉電視台直播節目被毆打，都令觀眾留下深刻印象，而梁克遜最後作品是2006年電影《黑拳》。<br />\n<br />\n記者問Vincent可知父親如何入行時，他說：「我記得佢講過係70年代喺街度被星探發掘拍廣告，應該係拍竹葉青，佢近10年8年，因為年紀大，所以少再拍嘢，係間中帶人做臨時演員。我爸爸以前喺楊協成做公關嘅，拍咗廣告之後，又拍吓電視同電影，試過有電視台搵佢簽約正式做演員，但爸爸唔想太困身，唔想簽死一間，鍾意兩邊走，後來佢set up咗間特約演員公司，但早幾年身體唔好已經冇做。」<br />\n<br />\n可知道父親生前最愛哪一部電影演出？Vincent說：「佢冇話特別鍾意邊部，不過間中都會提吓《國產凌凌漆》同《精裝追女仔II》，但佢戲份重啲係《第一把交椅》，另一部係同謝賢拍嘅亞視劇《千王之王重出江湖》，我爸爸鍾意拍戲，但又唔係話想做明星嗰種，佢話過自己半途出家，好enjoy呢份工作。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rgTEeduJSmy8hTfVTBHfB3UqckU=/802x615/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GEJYTIX7EREX3GSFPKIMOCV5DE.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrgTEeduJSmy8hTfVTBHfB3UqckU%3D%2F802x615%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGEJYTIX7EREX3GSFPKIMOCV5DE.JPG&h=2b4ce71a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1981年梁克遜拍「人人搬屋」廣告。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3RlGC8Wx50ajpRtfjqm-671jJLY=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JXP4NPWSC5BHVD6KT5RMIWJKWE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3RlGC8Wx50ajpRtfjqm-671jJLY%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJXP4NPWSC5BHVD6KT5RMIWJKWE.jpg&h=34c847ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《精裝追女仔II》演司徒銘議員。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201026/DTLDOTPEDRBFTHALE2Y6TB2NXI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201026%2FDTLDOTPEDRBFTHALE2Y6TB2NXI%2F&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETWWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=e934209c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201026%2FDTLDOTPEDRBFTHALE2Y6TB2NXI%2F&h=403ef423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201026/DTLDOTPEDRBFTHALE2Y6TB2NXI/</a>"},{"pid":"06b1e3dc46fe242b52edad0582cd4f2acb639bd1","tid":2259503,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T01:24:33.000Z","msg":"賴有為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127c2bca7a6f64b40d87392a6f6fff0bc492e995","tid":2259503,"uid":343361,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T01:26:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7521d4c3f98e1cd98edd598648de021fd44b63c4","tid":2259503,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T01:56:26.000Z","msg":"骰盅魔鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1841360999263025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1841360999263025&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETWWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=2997a760\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1841360999263025</a>"},{"pid":"69839a61fc88cd23144694944f57ac5cf9ac7d91","tid":2259503,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:14:06.000Z","msg":"白必圖"},{"pid":"886ba923c189ecec977d5b5a2073b1a3d2910976","tid":2259503,"uid":7323,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:27:47.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">大哥講話你要聽</span>"},{"pid":"c420640a6ee89df97aabdff5024e66578ac1348a","tid":2259503,"uid":5419,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:31:57.000Z","msg":"有啲似朱鎔基"},{"pid":"6c3b61a7ddb483657f3837f9bcb11e0c245960ef","tid":2259503,"uid":49588,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:37:45.000Z","msg":"佢拍既好多戲都有睇過"},{"pid":"68c15b1d6b39b909065d2e204643ce0869e6cef2","tid":2259503,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7521d4c3f98e1cd98edd598648de021fd44b63c4","tid":2259503,"